                    Deal?
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FAQ Section -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="mb-8 text-center text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
                Frequently asked questions
            </h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-5">
                    <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
                        Is it really one-time, or will you add a subscription later?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
                        It's really one-time. Your $29 gets you the current version and every future update. No
                        subscription, no "premium tier," no "wait, that feature costs extra." We're allergic to that
                        stuff.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-5">
                    <h3 class="mb-2 font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
                        Can I use it on more than two machines?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
                        The license covers two machines. If you need more (work laptop, home desktop, secret lair
                        computer, etc.), reach out to us â€” we're reasonable humans.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-border-subtle)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-5">
